[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 11/12 points, a Limit Raise in \Hs. So after the overcall 
he makes a Support Cue-bid of 2\S.

SOUTH adds her 16 to the 11 that NORTH has promised as a minimum and goes straight 
to 4\H.

If NORTH had significantly more than 11 he could bid on, but in this case he should happily pass.}

