[Student "S"]
{NORTH has the strength for a raise to game in \Ss, but this could be dangerous since SOUTH 
has overcalled rather than opened. Instead, NORTH shows her strength with a Support Cue-bid.

SOUTH in fact had a pretty good overcall so he jumps to 3\S and NORTH bids the game.

With a weak overcall SOUTH would have just returned to 2\S which NORTH would pass.}

